,"tid":2486863,"uid":265313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:06:07.000Z","msg":"邊行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:10:18.000Z","msg":"degree science乞食科"},{"pid":"2f13c521f1feebc7d0a8f050c64e85e7bb0f9cd4","tid":2486863,"uid":280593,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:11:43.000Z","msg":"去社會福利署"},{"pid":"47cb39262a62be465b0d203d6fbbf8d1fa218e61","tid":2486863,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4c79c4bd924c37d6aed68b9e9f92ceef4743bcf","tid":2486863,"uid":287107,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9e0ccc8c323d0803ee61f19eb6bf7721a2fe2bad","tid":2486863,"uid":242537,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:08:09.000Z","msg":"西九8樓啦<br />\n踎一個下午 飽到你嘔<br />\n唔洗我教啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/blah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:09:45.000Z","msg":"2手飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:11:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IkfemqLggy0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIkfemqLggy0&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DJriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=569ba0db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IkfemqLggy0</a>"},{"pid":"c09909c9745d094fcc152b2768cebeb67a6d1797","tid":2486863,"uid":242537,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:13:18.000Z","msg":"我們的互聯網，在助人尋美食的openrice，卻沒有教人搵二手飯的指南。事實上，香港雖然餐廳處處，但不是哪裡也有合適的二手飯，所以要做流浪者，就必須要對鄰近食肆有充掌握。<br />\n<br />\n餐廳1：麥當勞<br />\n<br />\n常見二手美食：薯條、薯餅、可樂、熱香餅、熱香餅專用蜜糖<br />\n<br />\n二手解讀：每位食客離開後，餐盤上幾乎例必留下前三款食物，如閣下是嗜炸物，保證能大快朵頣。熱香餅因有三塊之多，部分女食客可能會食剩一塊半塊，好運者甚至可發現少量豬柳漢堡！另要留意熱香餅用蜜糖，常有餅剩。踏入秋季唇乾舌燥，可充當真蜜糖沖水飲作滋潤喉嚨之用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n餐廳2：連鎖快餐廳(美心大家樂大快活均可)<br />\n<br />\n常見二手美食：咖哩牛腩飯、栗米肉粒飯(其化頹飯均合)大量白米飯、奶茶、伴碟菜<br />\n<br />\n二手解讀：咖哩牛飯可算是肉眼觀察中常見的二手飯，皆因薯仔太濟，牛腩太有咬口，雖然不少快餐店﹙如大快活﹚，其咖哩牛腩飯味道不錯，但七成以上人仍會食唔曬。至於被視為頹飯的栗米肉粒，往往是不少人揀無可揀之選，進食意慾不高，自然吃剩機會也大。另伴碟菜更是二手飯食客必食之選---伴碟菜由於只為點綴或「叫做有條菜」，通常白烚了事，因味同嚼蠟，所以食客通常棄之一旁。其實食菜有益，二手食客實不容錯過。<br />\n<br />\n建議在進店前，先看水牌，如見有咖哩牛腩和栗米肉粒，能飽餐一頓二手飯的機會勁大。"},{"pid":"78ec4f20a61d2b1fcf65133126199a75befd7227","tid":2486863,"uid":255474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"874e38399f4bea8f7910de635335cc6f97b3cd77","tid":2486863,"uid":186232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:05:36.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以比啖飯我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:13:27.000Z","msg":"剩返幾多錢"},{"pid":"db11ad1729c6dbcedff37768c53706b861711a34","tid":2486863,"uid":6777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:14:34.000Z","msg":"何不食肉糜"},{"pid":"ea65fb8308e5e348eba1b346f136d82b906f1171","tid":2486863,"uid":186232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"47cb39262a62be465b0d203d6fbbf8d1fa218e61","tid":2486863,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4c79c4bd924c37d6aed68b9e9f92ceef4743bcf","tid":2486863,"uid":287107,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9e0ccc8c323d0803ee61f19eb6bf7721a2fe2bad","tid":2486863,"uid":242537,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:08:09.000Z","msg":"西九8樓啦<br />\n踎一個下午 飽到你嘔<br />\n唔洗我教啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/blah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:09:45.000Z","msg":"2手飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:11:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IkfemqLggy0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIkfemqLggy0&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DJriIWE